                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony2-rest/edit/master/knpu/episode2/helpful-details-key.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Our end goal is to make our API easy to use so if something goes wrong our clients
can actually debug it without pulling their hair out or having to email us. </p>
<p>Whenever you throw an exception in PHP there is going to be a message, like
"No programmer found for username":</p>
